extends layout

block content

  link(href='/css/home.css', rel='stylesheet')

  .container
    .row.header
      .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6
        h1 Storming.ME
        p.lead Hacking the Tweetstorm with Pictures of Text
        a.btn.btn-info.btn-raised.btn-lg.login-btn(href="/login") Login with Twitter
      .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6
        .well.infobox
          p
            | The single greatest strength of Twitter has always been its simplicity.
            | There's a lot to be said in 140 characters. But there's even more that
            | just needs more space.
          p
            | Storming.ME allows you to compose a tweet with no character limit and 
            | post it as a image.
          a.btn.btn-default.example-btn(href="https://twitter.com/karangoel/status/546098580096704513", target="_blank", style="margin-right:8px;") Example Tweet
          a.btn.btn-default.why-btn(href="https://medium.com/five-hundred-words/hacking-the-tweet-stream-52ed63a0731", target="_blank") Why Storming.ME
    .row
      .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-body
            h2 No Character Limit
            i.icon.mdi-action-subject
            p Compose and post a tweet with 
              b no character limit
              | . So now get the message across in as many words as it takes.
      .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-body
            h2 Higher Engagement
            i.icon.mdi-social-group-add
            p Tweets with media have proven to be more engaging. Even 
              a(href="https://twitter.com/cdixon/status/535256285500178433", target="_blank") Chris Dixon
              |  agrees. Tweets created using Storming.ME will be loved by your followers.
      .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-body
            H2 Fully Responsive
            i.icon.mdi-hardware-phonelink
            p Storming.ME has a perfectly responsive dashboard where you can compose your 
              | tweetstorm conveniently on any device.
  
  include footer
